 str, `AssetCode` str, `Reference` str, `AccruedDays` str, `AccruedInterest` str, `AggregateQuantity` str\n\n### External (columns 1–22)\n`RecordId` str, `Destination` str, `Terminal` str, `MessageNo` str, `Account` str, `Source` str, `Custodian` str, `FromDate` date (dd/MM/yyyy), `ToDate` date (dd/MM/yyyy), `StatementBasis` str, `Quantity` decimal, `LongShort` str, `PositionValue` decimal, `PositionDate` date (dd/MM/yyyy), `Price` decimal, `Currency` str, `PreparationDate` date (dd/MM/yyyy), `PriceQuotationDate` date (dd/MM/yyyy), `AssetType` str, `AssetDescription` str, `AssetCode` str, `TransformMessageId` str\n\n> `Destination`, `Terminal`, `MessageNo`, `TransformMessageId` are External-only fields; `Reference`, `AccruedDays`, `AccruedInterest`, `AggregateQuantity` are Internal-only fields.\n\n---\n\n## Enrichments (both feeds)\n\n| Field | Rule |\n|---|---|\n| `System` | `\"Internal\"` (Internal feed) / `\"External\"` (External feed) |\n| `AssetID` | `lookup(\"assetLookup\", AssetCode)` |\n| `AccountID` | `lookup(\"accountLookup\", Account)` |\n\n---\n\n## Lookups\n\n| Alias Name | Source File | Used In |\n|---|---|---|\n| `assetLookup` | assetLookup.csv | `AssetID` ← `AssetCode` (both feeds) |\n| `accountLookup` | accountLookup.csv | `AccountID` ← `Account` (both feeds) |\n\nBoth are auto-updating file-based lookup tables.\n\n---\n\n## Matching Logic (NetGroup / M01Match)\n\n### Group Trigger\n- Records enter a group when `count > 0`.\n\n### Projection Keys (join dimensions)\nRecords are grouped together when **all** of the following match:\n\n| Key Field | Type |\n|---|---|\n| `AccountID` | str |\n| `Custodian` | str |\n| `LongShort` | str |\n| `Currency` | str |\n| `AssetType` | str |\n| `AssetDescription` | str |\n| `PositionDate` | date |\n\n### Computed Functions (evaluated within each group)\n\n| Function | Rule |\n|---|---|\n| `NetQuantity` | `sum(Quantity where System=\"Internal\") − sum(Quantity where System=\"External\")` |\n| `NetPositionValue` | `sum(PositionValue where System=\"Internal\") − sum(PositionValue where System=\"External\")` |\n\n### Confidence Outcomes\n\n| Name | Trigger Rule | Action |\n|---|---|---|\n| **NetToZero** | `NetQuantity = 0` AND some records have `System=\"Internal\"` AND some have `System=\"External\"` | MATCH |\n| **NetBreak** | `NetQuantity ≠ 0` AND some records have `System=\"Internal\"` AND some have `System=\"External\"` | Raise exception → **Break** |\n\n> No tolerance is defined; `NetQuantity = 0` is exact.\n\n---\n\n## Break / Exception Conditions\n\n### Exception Type: `Break`\n- **Structure trigger:** `count > 1` (within the matched group)\n- **Fields carried on the Break exception:**\n\n| Field | Type | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| `netQuantity` | decimal | `NetQuantity` function |\n| `netPositionValue` | decimal | `NetPositionValue` function |\n| `sameCurrency` | bool | Uniformity check across grouped records |\n| `samePositionDate` | bool | Uniformity check |\n| `sameLongShort` | bool | Uniformity check |\n| `sameAssetType` | bool | Uniformity check |\n| `sameAssetDescription` | bool | Uniformity check |\n| `sameCustodian` | bool | Uniformity check |\n| `samePrice` | bool | Uniformity check |\n| `sameAccountID` | bool | Uniformity check |\n| `ExceptionReasonCode` | str | Editable; decoded via **ReasonCodes** decode set; default `\"Please select...\"` |\n| `ExceptionResolutionCode` | str | Editable; decoded via **ResolutionCodes** decode set; default `\"Please select...\"` |\n\n---\n\n## Decode Sets Affecting Break Values\n\n| Field | Decode Set |\n|---|---|\n| `ExceptionReasonCode` | `ReasonCodes` |\n| `ExceptionResolutionCode` | `ResolutionCodes` |\n\n> Decode set contents are not defined in this XML; verify externally.\n\n---\n\n## Unmatched / One-Sided Records\nNo explicit confidence rule is defined for groups containing records from only one system (Internal-only or External-only). Such groups will not satisfy either `NetToZero` or `NetBreak` (both require presence of both sides) and will remain unresolved.\n\n### Database Schema (vanguardpospositionspoc)\nSchema: vanguardpospositionspoc — 53 tables\n\nvanguardpospositionspoc.assignedrole (3 columns):\n  pk (bytea)\n  roleid (bytea)\n  taskid (bytea)\n\nvanguardpospositionspoc.assigneduser (3 columns):\n  pk (bytea)\n  userid (bytea)\n  taskid (bytea)\n\nvanguardpospositionspoc.auditgrouprecordlink (3 columns):\n  pk (bytea)\n  recordpk (bytea)\n  grouppk (bytea)\n\nvanguardpospositionspoc.auditgroups (9 columns):\n  pk (bytea)\n  datetimestamp (timestamp with time zone)\n  timestampzoneid (integer, nullable)\n  activestatus (integer)\n  matchstatus (integer)\n  groupname (character varying)\n  matchname (character varying)\n  confidence (character varying)\n  actiontypeid (integer)\n\nvanguardpospositionspoc.audittaskoutcomes (9 columns):\n  pk (bytea)\n  auditpk (bytea)\n  datetimestamp (timestamp with time zone)\n  timestampzoneid (integer, nullable)\n  completed (timestamp with time zone, nullable)\n  outcome (character varying, nullable)\n  sessionid (bytea)\n  status (integer, nullable)\n  taskfqn (character varying, nullable)\n\nvanguardpospositionspoc.autoaction (6 columns):\n  pk (bytea)\n  description (character varying, nullable)\n  scope (text)\n  scopedescription (text)\n  enabled (boolean)\n  position (integer)\n\nvanguardpospositionspoc.autoactionaudit (9 columns):\n  pk (bytea)\n  autoaction (bytea)\n  datetimecreated (timestamp with time zone)\n  createdby (character varying)\n  lastmodified (timestamp with time zone, nullable)\n  modifiedby (character varying, nullable)\n  laststatuschange (timestamp with time zone, nullable)\n  statuschangedby (character varying, nullable)\n  lastapplied (timestamp with time zone, nullable)\n\nvanguardpospositionspoc.autoactionhistory (9 columns):\n  pk (bytea)\n  autoactionpk (bytea)\n  auditid (bytea)\n  datetimestamp (timestamp with time zone)\n  description (character varying, nullable)\n  scope (text)\n  scopedescription